## Who Built This

This tool was designed by Paul Statchen, working collaboratively across three AI systems:

- **Claude** (Anthropic) — primary build partner, tool architecture, legal translation layer
- **ChatGPT** (OpenAI) — contributed to early development
- **Gemini Pro** (Google) — contributed to early development

Three competing AI systems collaborated on a civic commons tool. That is the proof of concept. The technology exists. The will exists. The only question is whether the platforms will make it easy.

